videos.headline: Ohio State strikes first behind Garrett Wilson's diving TD
videos.description: C.J. Stroud connects with Garrett Wilson for a 21-yard touchdown to get Ohio State on the board early.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ohio State strikes first behind Garrett Wilson's diving TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue's O'Connell drops in 25-yard dime to Anthrop for the TD
videos.description: Aidan O'Connell finds Jackson Anthrop open for a 25-yard touchdown for the Boilermakers.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdue's O'Connell drops in 25-yard dime to Anthrop for the TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: OSU's TreVeyon Henderson forces his way in for a TD
videos.description: TreVeyon Henderson forces his way into the end zone from three yards out for an Ohio State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (OSU's TreVeyon Henderson forces his way in for a TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: TreVeyon Henderson cashes in on Purdue's fumble with a 57-yard TD
videos.description: Ohio State's Jerron Cage recovers a fumble, and TreVeyon Henderson follows up with a long touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (TreVeyon Henderson cashes in on Purdue's fumble with a 57-yard TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stroud catches Purdue's D sleeping for a wide-open TD
videos.description: C.J. Stroud finds Jaxon Smith-Njigba wide open in the end zone for an Ohio State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stroud catches Purdue's D sleeping for a wide-open TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Garrett Wilson's phenomenal TD catch puts Ohio State up big
videos.description: Ohio State capitalizes on Purdue's botched kickoff return with a 12-yard touchdown catch from Garrett Wilson.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Garrett Wilson's phenomenal TD catch puts Ohio State up big) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Garrett Wilson burns Purdue's D with 51-yard house call
videos.description: Garrett Wilson's third touchdown of the day gives Ohio State a 42-14 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Garrett Wilson burns Purdue's D with 51-yard house call) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Garrett Wilson stiff-arms Purdue DE for stellar TD
videos.description: OSU's Garrett Wilson hands out a mean stiff-arm on his way to the end zone for his fourth touchdown of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Garrett Wilson stiff-arms Purdue DE for stellar TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jackson Anthrop hauls in his second TD of the day for Purdue
videos.description: Aidan O'Connell connects with Jackson Anthrop for a nine-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jackson Anthrop hauls in his second TD of the day for Purdue) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chris Olave dives for the pylon to keep Ohio State rolling
videos.description: C.J. Stroud connects with Chris Olave for the 5-yard touchdown to give Ohio State a 59-31 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chris Olave dives for the pylon to keep Ohio State rolling) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Purdue WR drops perfectly-placed TD dime
videos.description: David Bell beats Ohio State's coverage but can't reel in the pass from Aidan O'Connell.

videos.headline: C.J. Stroud tosses five TDs as Ohio State rolls over Purdue
videos.description: C.J. Stroud throws five touchdown passes to lead Ohio State to a dominant 59-31 win over Purdue.
